cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.DS 

The paper focuses on machine learning approaches for forecasting demand in ride-hailing services, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence and machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves spatio-temporal estimation, which suggests that it may fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the paper involves statistical analysis and comparison of different models, which suggests that it may also fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
